""" MORE AWESOME HOTKEYS
" Run the q macro
nnoremap <leader>q @q

" bind H to toggle cursor highlighting
:nnoremap H :set cursorline! cursorcolumn!<CR>

"Map Ctrl + S to save in any mode
noremap <silent> <C-S>          :update<CR>
